         W   rotate view up
         S   rotate view down
         A   rotate view left
         D   rotate view right

        Up   move forward
      Down   move backward
      Left   strafe left
     Right   strafe right
  Shift+Up   move up
Shift+Down   move down
         T   reset user position

         F   toggle edit mode
 Left-Ctrl   enter select mode, if in edit mode
     Space   draw (edit mode) or add selection point (select mode)

         Z   delete the currently-selected region
         X   cut the currently-selected region
         C   copy the currently-selected region
         V   paste the currently-selected region

         I   shift cursor up
         K   shift cursor down
         J   shift cursor left
         L   shift cursor right
   Shift+I   shift cursor forward
   Shift+K   shift cursor down
         P   reset cursor offset

         Q   create a Cube cube
         [   decrease Cube cube radius
         ]   increase Cube cube radius
         .   increase Cube cube density
         ,   decrease Cube cube density
         /   reset Cube cube density

         1   stop simulation
         3   run simulation
         e   step simulation forward
         r   reset simulation
       Esc   quit program

         b   toggle performance info display
         g   toggle skybox drawing

         =   increase Cube base hue
         -   decrease Cube base hue
         n   toggle Cube flat shading